Class StringAtom

java.lang.Object
com.bhoffpauir.blisp.lib.Atom<String>
com.bhoffpauir.blisp.lib.StringAtom
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<StringAtom>
public class StringAtom extends Atom<String> implements Comparable<StringAtom>
Represents a string atom in blisp, using String as its value. In blisp, strings are enclosed in double quotes.

The StringAtom class extends Atom<String> and implements Comparable<StringAtom>, allowing string atoms to be compared and stored in ordered collections.

The class includes functionality for equality testing, string comparison, and regular expression pattern matching for valid strings in the language.
